  correct_answer = 'C',
  explanation = 'The author uses the word "misunderstanding" to criticize the way that many people think about the author''s home country. The author believes that these people are focusing on outdated and inaccurate representations of the country, and that they are failing to see the country''s more modern and complex reality. The passage states that "The author''s main purpose in this passage is to demonstrate that many of the stories that have been told about the autho…", which is the textual anchor for eliminating weaker choices. Choice C is correct because it aligns with that evidence: criticize the way that many people think about the author''s home country.. Each incorrect option either contradicts a explicit detail, imports information not present in the text, or answers a different question than the one asked.',
