UPDATE public.questions SET
  stimulus_text = 'The development of the computer has changed the way we communicate with one another. Before the Internet, people relied on letters, telegrams, and phone calls to stay in touch. Now, with the advent of instant messaging, video conferencing, and social media, we can communicate with anyone, anywhere, at any time. This is a revolutionary change that has had a profound impact on our lives. However, the widespread use of technology has also raised concerns about privacy and security. What are the benefits and drawbacks of this change in communication?',
