  correct_answer = 'B',
  explanation = 'The writer mentions earlier communication methods to give the reader a sense of how communication has changed over time. The writer is setting up a comparison between the past and the present to show how the development of the internet has dramatically changed the way we communicate. This historical context helps the reader understand the significance of the internet and its impact on our lives. The passage states that "The development of the computer has changed the way we communicate with one another. Before the Internet, people relied …", which is the textual anchor for eliminating weaker choices. Choice B is correct because it aligns with that evidence: To provide historical context for the development of modern communication technologies.. Each incorrect option either contradicts a explicit detail, imports information not present in the text, or answers a different question than the one asked.',
